metadata.description: Jennifer Clancy from Phoenix founded ALLE Learning™ in 2013. The mission of ALLE Learning™ is to enhance the quality of life for residents of all senior adult living facilities and communities across the United States, and the world. ALLE Learning™ is a leading provider of on-site turn-key educational programs for senior adult communities. In 2016, the company launched ALLE Online™. ALLE Online™ is a lifelong learning platform that provides complete classes for activity staff and life enrichment directors. It also provides support material for activity staff and life enrichment directors, the team of professionals with everything they need to plan, and deliver a lifelong learning program and free of charge, a helpful brochure titled Ten Ways to Implement Lifelong Learning Today.
